# Internal development docs — specs, plans, handoffs, proposals, backlog.
# These are design/dev artifacts, NOT shipped with the plugin; marketplace
# users get README + CHANGELOG. Excluded wholesale, matching the sibling
# deep-suite plugins (deep-review / deep-wiki / deep-evolve / deep-docs).
# ⚠️ Never blanket-unignore `docs/` — internal backlog has leaked publicly
#    before when the whole tree was tracked. If a doc must ship, link it
#    from README or relocate it out of docs/.
docs/

# Test artifacts
coverage/
*.lcov
.nyc_output/

# Editor
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# Scratch / temp
*.tmp
*.log
*.bak
